8
00:00:25,604 --> 00:00:27,805
This is the toughest time
in Marshall's life

9
00:00:27,806 --> 00:00:29,540
and I feel
absolutely useless.

10
00:00:29,541 --> 00:00:31,509
What can we do
to help?

11
00:00:31,510 --> 00:00:32,643
Don't look at me.

12
00:00:32,644 --> 00:00:34,478
This morning Marshall said,
"I have to pee."

13
00:00:34,479 --> 00:00:36,864
And I, "Don't worry, baby,
I'll do it for you."

14
00:00:36,865 --> 00:00:37,982
Halfway through the pee,

15
