I'm, like, "This doesn't
even make sense!"

16
00:00:39,684 --> 00:00:41,652
Well, uh, I've been
to a couple funerals,

17
00:00:41,653 --> 00:00:44,288
so I know my role:
I'm Vice Girl.

18
00:00:44,289 --> 00:00:46,190
Whatever Marshall needs
to get through this day,

19
