57
00:02:00,231 --> 00:02:02,533
Uh... Claws,
paws, talons,

58
00:02:02,534 --> 00:02:04,535
hooves, beaks and
clenched monkey fists.

59
00:02:04,536 --> 00:02:06,036
We can do this!

60
00:02:06,037 --> 00:02:07,838
Hey, guys, sorry, uh...
I left my charger back

61
