minutes chasing a cartoon fox.

72
00:02:29,594 --> 00:02:31,762
"Spoonful of sugar..."?

73
00:02:31,763 --> 00:02:33,330
Grow up.

74
00:02:33,832 --> 00:02:36,400
I'm so sorry
for your loss, Judy.

75
00:02:36,401 --> 00:02:41,739
Thank you, Reverend.

76
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:43,674
Unfortunately, I can't.

77
