become a reverend.

91
00:03:15,607 --> 00:03:18,509
Yeah, well, your lunch money
finally ran out.

92
00:03:18,510 --> 00:03:20,210
Kidding!

93
00:03:20,946 --> 00:03:23,981
Marshall Eriksen,
you could use a laugh.

94
00:03:23,982 --> 00:03:25,816
Yeah!

95
00:03:25,817 --> 00:03:28,485
This video is entitled,
"Little League Coach Gets Hit in

96
