Vomits in a Garbage Can."

97
00:03:31,423 --> 00:03:34,191
I don't wanna give anything
away. Let's just watch.

98
00:03:34,192 --> 00:03:35,893
(bat connects with ball,
man groans, vomits)

99
00:03:35,894 --> 00:03:37,928
BOTH:
Oh!

100
00:03:37,929 --> 00:03:39,296
(chuckling)

101
00:03:39,297 --> 00:03:41,131
See? 'Cause,
'cause he got hit...

102
00:03:41,132 --> 00:03:42,466
...right in the nuts,

103
00:03:42,467 --> 00:03:45,502
BOTH:
The fat kid just runs away.

104
00:03:45,503 --> 00:03:47,437
Trey Platt.

105
00:03:48,173 --> 00:03:49,306
I can't believe

106
00:03:49,307 --> 00:03:51,308
my father's funeral service is
being led

107
00:03:51,309 --> 00:03:53,644
by Trey "The Noogie Machine"
Platt.

108
00:03:53,645 --> 00:03:55,012
That guy gave you noogies?

109
00:03:55,013 --> 00:03:56,880
What, did he carry
a stepladder?

110
00:03:56,881 --> 00:03:59,650
He made me carry it.

111
00:04:00,452 --> 00:04:02,753
So, my dad has these questions
he asks to help create

112
00:04:02,754 --> 00:04:05,823
