and meaningful?

220
00:08:49,603 --> 00:08:51,204
I mean, who can
live up to that?

221
00:08:51,205 --> 00:08:52,438
BARNEY:
Exactly.

222
00:08:52,439 --> 00:08:53,873
All those "famous
last word""

223
00:08:53,874 --> 00:08:55,908
