248
00:10:05,913 --> 00:10:07,813
Whoa.
Are you okay?

249
00:10:07,814 --> 00:10:08,815
Listen!

250
00:10:08,816 --> 00:10:11,117
(yawns)

251
00:10:11,118 --> 00:10:14,120
I'm gonna go take a nap.

252
00:10:14,121 --> 00:10:17,823
