and it's all because of me!

253
00:10:17,824 --> 00:10:21,260
Guys, I have a role:
I'm Judy's bitch! Yeah!

254
00:10:21,261 --> 00:10:22,728
Well, but this day is

255
00:10:22,729 --> 00:10:23,830
